  <em>Last updated: September 10, 2025</em>

  <p>This privacy policy explains how Enköpings Rehabcenter collects, uses, and protects your personal data in accordance with GDPR (General Data Protection Regulation).</p>

  <h2>What information do we collect?</h2>

  <h3>From contact forms:</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>Name, email address, phone number</li>
    <li>Messages and questions you send us</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Technical information (automatically):</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>IP address and browser information</li>
    <li>Pages you visit on our website</li>
    <li>Time spent on the website</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>How do we use your information?</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>To respond to your questions</strong> and provide the care you need</li>
    <li><strong>To improve our website</strong> through anonymous analysis</li>
    <li><strong>To comply with legal requirements</strong> in healthcare</li>
  </ul>

  <p>We never share your information with third parties without your consent, except when required by law.</p>

  <h2>Your rights under GDPR</h2>

  <p>You have the right to:</p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Access</strong> your personal data</li>
    <li><strong>Rectify incorrect data</strong></li>
    <li><strong>Erase your data</strong> ("the right to be forgotten")</li>
    <li><strong>Restrict the processing</strong> of your data</li>
    <li><strong>Data portability</strong> - receive your data in a portable format</li>
    <li><strong>Object to the processing</strong> of your data</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Cookies and tracking</h2>

  <p>We only use necessary cookies for website functionality. For analytics, we use Google Analytics only with your consent.</p>

  <p>You can change your cookie settings at any time by clicking "Cookie settings" at the bottom of the page.</p>

  <h2>How long do we store your information?</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Contact details</strong>: Stored until you ask us to delete them or 3 years after last contact</li>
    <li><strong>Analytics data</strong>: Anonymized after 26 months</li>
    <li><strong>Medical information</strong>: Follows healthcare regulations (up to 10 years)</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Security</h2>

  <p>We implement appropriate technical and organizational measures to protect your personal data against unauthorized access, loss, or destruction.</p>

  <h2>Contact</h2>

  <p>If you have questions about this policy or want to exercise your rights?</p>

  <p><strong>Enköpings Rehabcenter</strong><br />
  Email: info@enkopingsrehabcenter.se<br />
  Phone: Contact us via the website<br />
  Address: Enköping, Sweden</p>

  <p>You can also contact us through our website's contact form.</p>
